---
Prompt all gives you a default prompt.

 %h for current HP. %H for maximum HP.

 %m for current mana. %M for maximum mana.

 %v for current move. %V for maximum move.

 %C for current combo count.

 %I for current chi.

 %A for current Arcane Power (mage/sorcerer/wizard/grand master stacking bonus).

 %P for current Holy Power (cleric/paladin/priest/templar stacking bonus).

 %Q for current Mental Power (psi/nec/ego/kin stacking bonus). See HELP MENTAL-POWER.

 %b for current bloodlust (vampires only). %B for max bloodlust.

 %g for gold. %x for experience.

 %a for alignment. %r for room name. %s for stance name.

 %t for current time of day.

 %F for wolf form (HUMANUS/LUPIS/GAROU, werewolves only).

 %c for a newline in the prompt.

 %% for a literal percent sign.
